Revision history for Config-PlConfig

0.1_02 Tue  Sep 11 11:56:12 2007
      - Moved functionality from pldefaults to Config::PlConfig::DotScheme
      - save() now takes a hashref to save as optional argument.
      - Support for autosave.
         (Global:  use Config::PlConfig qw(:autosave);
          Lexical: $c = Config::PlConfig->new({autosave => 1 });)

0.1_01  Mon Aug  6 19:35:31 2007
       Initial release.

